CRISIS! CATASTROPHE!
EXPOSURE WILL CAUSE
CANCER AND BIRTH DEFECTS!
THE LAND CONTAMINATED FOR
GENERATIONS! TENS OF
THOUSANDS COULD DIE
TOXIC PLUMES FROM AN ENERGy
PLANT THREATEN AN ENTIRE REGION!
DEAD ZONE
NOTHING, MARK.
TS A COAL PLANT
IN APPALACHIA
OUR CORRESPONDENT IS NEAR
THE LEAK. AMy, WHAT ARE
OFFICIALS DOING TO EVACUATE
THE AREA?
BACK
TO You
BORS
